section.section:
As a condition of licensure, each facility shall adopt written policies and procedures to implement the requirements of §§ 10-701 through 10-709 of this article. The policies and procedures:
May expand the rights provided in §§ 10-701 through 10-709 of this article;
Shall provide for a mechanism for patients and others to report suspected violations of §§ 10-701 through 10-709 of this article to a designated official of the hospital;
Shall provide a system for investigating suspected violations; and
Shall ensure that there is a timely appropriate response to any suspected violation.
